{"article_id":"gZJZjvZnJTE2Az5c","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell announced Monday night","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"he does not have the votes","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"he needs","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"to pass the second draft of a Republican health care bill .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"Instead , Republicans plan to vote for straight repeal , with a two-year delay .","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"( File photo is a screen grab from C-SPAN )","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"( CNSNews.com ) -","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"\" Regretfully , it is now apparent that the effort","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"to repeal and immediately replace the failure of Obamacare","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"will not be successful , \"","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"( R-Ky. )","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"announced on Monday night .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"His statement follows the defection of two more Republicans","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"- Sens . Jerry Moran","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"( R-Kan. )","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"and Mike Lee","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"( R-Utah. ) .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"Sen. Rand Paul","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"( R-Ky. )","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"has firmly opposed the bill all along ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"it does not repeal the \" fundamental flaw \" of Obamacare .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"And Sen. Susan Collins","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"( R-Maine )","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"said","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"she would vote no","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"because of `` sweeping and deep cuts '' to Medicaid .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"With 50 votes","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"needed for passage ,","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"and only 52 Republican senators , the bill stood no chance with four `` nays . ''","depth":4},{"id":31,"text":"McConnell said","depth":5},{"id":32,"text":"the Senate , \" in the coming days , \" will vote to take up a House bill","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"repealing Obamacare ,","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"but with a two-year delay ,","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"to give Republicans more time","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"to come up with a replacement .","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"This is the same House bill","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"that Republicans overwhelmingly passed in 2015 ,","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"and which then-President Obama vetoed .","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"( In his veto message , President Obama said","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"the Affordable Care Act \" is working . \" )","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"McConnell on Monday said","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"the Republican goal remains the same :","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"to establish a \" patient-centered health care system","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"that gives Americans access to quality , affordable care . \"","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"But the Senate bill , draft number two , does not deliver such a system ,","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"Republican critics say :","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"\" In addition to not repealing all of the Obamacare taxes ,","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"it doesn ' t go far enough","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"in lowering premiums for middle class families ;","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"nor does it create enough free space from the most costly Obamacare regulations , \"","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"Sen. Mike Lee said in a statement","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"announcing his \" no \" vote .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"Sen. Jerry Moran said","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"he wants to repeal and replace Obamacare ,","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"but the bill","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"produced by Senate leaders behind closed doors","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"\" fails to repeal the Affordable Care Act","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"or address healthcare ' s rising costs .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"\" For the same reasons","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"I could not support the previous version of this bill ,","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"I can not support this one , \"","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"Moran said .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"\" We should not put our stamp of approval on bad policy .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"Furthermore ,","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"if we leave the federal government in control of everyday healthcare decisions ,","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"it is more likely that our healthcare system will devolve into a single-payer system ,","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"which would require a massive federal spending increase . \"","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"Moran called for a fresh start ,","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"including an \" open legislative process . \"","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"Sen. John McCain","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"( R-Ariz. ) ,","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"recovering at home in Arizona from surgery","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"to remove a blood clot ,","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"urged his colleagues not to \" repeat the original mistakes","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"that led to the failure of Obamacare . ''","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"\" One of the major problems with Obamacare was that it was written on a strict party-line basis","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"and driven through Congress","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"without a single Republican vote , \"","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"McCain said .","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"\" The Congress must now return to regular order ,","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"hold hearings ,","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"receive input from members of both parties ,","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"and heed the recommendations of our nation 's governors","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"so that we can produce a bill","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"that finally provides Americans with access to quality and affordable health care . \"","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"Conservatives were divided on the current version of the Better Care Reconciliation Act .","depth":4},{"id":88,"text":"The Family Research Council supported it ,","depth":6},{"id":89,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"it would end President Obama ' s \" legacy of taxpayer-funded abortion in health care . \"","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"But ForAmerica President David Bozell called the Republican bill a \" hack job . \"","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"\" You could see Senate Republicans ' lack of a replacement plan strategy from a mile away .","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"Make no mistake :","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"The Trump voter does not blame Trump ,","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"but rather the feckless leaders in the Republican Establishment .","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"This bill was a betrayal of every campaign ad and promise","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"the Republican Party ran on for seven years , \"","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"Bozell said in a statement .","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"In a tweet","depth":6},{"id":100,"text":"issued Monday night ,","depth":6},{"id":101,"text":"President Trump said ,","depth":5},{"id":102,"text":"\" Republicans should just REPEAL failing ObamaCare now","depth":5},{"id":103,"text":"& work on a new Healthcare Plan","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"that will start from a clean slate .","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"Dems will join in ! \"","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":211,"left":136,"right":210,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":112,"right":135,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":112,"left":110,"right":111,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":109,"right":4,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":109,"left":0,"right":108,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":108,"left":1,"right":107,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":111,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"par